plot: Lex tasks Supergirl with protecting Andrea from an anti-tech extremist; Lena moves forward with Non Nocere, with Lex's help.

Lex forces Supergirl to protect Andrea from an anti-tech extremist as Andrea prepares to roll out Platinum Obsidian. Alex goes through her first day of being on her own rather than with the DEO, Lex tries to forge a partnership with Leviathan, and Kara considers whether refusing to accept William's dinner invitation was a mistake.—Gislef
